PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1987-2592 that removes the references to the inclusion of the subsurface mines and minerals in respect of a small piece of land situated near the Cascade Power Station in BANFF NATIONAL PARK that is to be acquired from the Canadian Pacific Railway Company in an exchange of lands provided for therein.
